,Recommended,225080,9722324,"Posted: 4 April, 2014",all,Halflight,"Brothers - A Tale of Two Sons is a puzzle platform game that gives you control of two brothers while they search for a mystical medicine able to save their father from death.The game allows you to command the two boys at once taking advantage of the mandatory controller input. While the whole button scheme can appear complex at the beginning, it quickly grows very comfortable to the player after some minutes in. Brothers is also able to use the simple premise of the gameplay to issue you more and more original challenges as you progress in the game, never giving you the feeling you are doing the same thing over and over again.While the artistic direction is pretty gorgeous and gives away a distinct fairy tale vibe and the writing isn't afraid of getting darker and darker as the boys' quest advances, Brothers - A Tale of Two sons is remarkably short: I was able to clear it in under four hours. Still, the title is definetly worth a shot"
