,Recommended,225080,8921675,"Posted: 31 January, 2014",all,Yeonni,"This game. Is. So. Amazing. I think I broke something. Like my head.This is what you get when a game's looks, gameplay and story go perfectly together, to the point where you can't tell where one ends and the other begins. It's short, but those two hours I spent on this game is worth a hundred in another, I *swear*. The graphics are beautiful and set the mood, the story is fantastically told (I can't properly do justice to how it pulled me in sneakily and then knocked me out), and the gameplay is smooth and fresh. And the sound; both the (wordless) voice acting and the music are probably half the reason I got so incredibly in there. With something that looks and feels very very simple, these people have created a work of art.A must to play, no nonsense."
